1. *Stvarnost* je često surova i nepravedna. (Reality is often harsh and unfair.)
2. Ukoliko želite da promenite svoju *stvarnost*, morate promeniti svoje misli i postupke. (If you want to change your reality, you need to change your thoughts and actions.)
3. On je potpuno izgubio kontakt sa *stvarnošću*. (He has completely lost touch with reality.)
4. Njihova veza je bila bolja u *stvarnosti* nego u snovima. (Their relationship was better in reality than in dreams.)
5. *Stvarnost* nas je sustigla, moramo se suočiti sa posledicama naših odluka. (Reality has caught up with us, we must face the consequences of our decisions.)
6. Ljudi često biraju da žive u *stvarnosti* ili u svetu mašte. (People often choose to live in reality or in the world of imagination.)
7. Iako je bila nezgodna, situacija je bila bolja od *stvarnosti* koju je zamišljao. (Although it was inconvenient, the situation was better than the reality he imagined.)
8. *Stvarnost* nije uvek ono što se čini. (Reality is not always what it seems.)
9. Knjiga je prepuna čudesnih ideja koje mogu promeniti našu *stvarnost*. (The book is full of wonderful ideas that can change our reality.)
10. *Stvarnost* nas tera da budemo jaki i izdržljivi. (Reality forces us to be strong and resilient.)